race.comment: Competitive. WINGED (5) spiked his figures placing at Narromine over this trip. Can use the rails gate to advantage and tumbles in weight this grade with the claim atop. That brings him right into it. SEMECO (7) peaks off a close-up effort at Muswellbrook over 1450m. Has placed 4/5 over a mile and hits this race at peak fitness. A player. EJECT (2) delivered a CL1 at Moree this trip and then got too far back at Armidale when he dropped back to a sprint freshened. Maps well and can get back on track. MARNOO (8) was beaten 3L in the WINGED race and also appreciated the step up in trip. Has the winkers on for the first time and can improve into the finish. COELLA (1) is hard to catch but she's been racing in stronger and would be a hope putting her best foot forward. Finally draws an inside barrier.
